    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_4131-4160",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4131-4160",
      "markText": "她是棵树，一直向着一个亮灯的窗户长高，终于够得到窥视窗内。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4131&rangeEnd=4160",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4131&rangeEnd=4160"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_5_10547-10589",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10547-10589",
      "markText": "盲婚如同博彩，获胜的机会尽管渺茫，究竟是每一个人都有希望，尤其在婚姻尚且遥远的时候。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10547&rangeEnd=10589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10547&rangeEnd=10589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_1219-1262",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1219-1262",
      "markText": "她们躲在一个窗户后面张望，撅着臀部，圆鼓鼓的仿佛要胀破提花绸袴，粗辫子顺着乳沟垂下来。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1219&rangeEnd=1262",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1219&rangeEnd=1262"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_3196-3232",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3196-3232",
      "markText": "在四小姐看来这又是少帅的一个可敬之处，说起来，他是以自己的人生偿还父债。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3196&rangeEnd=3232",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3196&rangeEnd=3232"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_10705-10756",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10705-10756",
      "markText": "他蜷身侧卧，忽然看上去很平凡，很陌生，是新造的第一个男子，可以是任何人，根本不值得费那么多工夫来制作。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10705&rangeEnd=10756",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10705&rangeEnd=10756"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_3101-3127",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3101-3127",
      "markText": "他的妻子很平凡，寡言少语，比他大四岁，相貌还要见老。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3101&rangeEnd=3127",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3101&rangeEnd=3127"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_1620-1646",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1620-1646",
      "markText": "要是碰巧还又年青又斯文，看上去就是国家唯一的指望了。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1620&rangeEnd=1646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1620&rangeEnd=1646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_5_5073-5115",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5073-5115",
      "markText": "“大蛤蟆。”一屋子喃喃低语。无人敢赞赏勤务兵的急才。首任大总统的面容说穿了确实神似。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5073&rangeEnd=5115",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5073&rangeEnd=5115"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_6_580-650",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "580-650",
      "markText": "但是在陈家的这些热闹中常常会有这么一刻，盛大的日子在她身边荡荡流过，平滑中略有起伏，仿佛一条太阳晒暖的大河，无论做什么事都会辜负这样的时光。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=580&rangeEnd=650",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=580&rangeEnd=650"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_5006-5082",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5006-5082",
      "markText": "他探身掸了掸烟灰，别过头来吻她，一只鹿在潭边漫不经心啜了口水。额前垂着一绺子头发，头向她俯过来，像乌云蔽天，又像山间直罩下来的夜色。她晕眩地坠入黑暗中。",
      "totalCount": 100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5006&rangeEnd=5082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5006&rangeEnd=5082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_8_3889-3951",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3889-3951",
      "markText": "可惜她不能走进他没有她的那些年：一个个荒凉的庭院，被古老的太阳晒成了黄色。她要一路跑进去，大声喊着“我在这儿！我在这儿呀！”",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3889&rangeEnd=3951",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3889&rangeEnd=3951"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_3658-3673",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3658-3673",
      "markText": "你不一样。我们会永远在一起的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3658&rangeEnd=3673",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3658&rangeEnd=3673"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_4_2199-2269",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2199-2269",
      "markText": "两块狭长的胭脂从眼皮一直抹到下巴，烘托出雪白的琼瑶鼻。武生的彩脸看上去异常阔大，像个妖魔的面具，唱腔也瓮声瓮气，仿佛是从陶面具底下发出声音。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2199&rangeEnd=2269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2199&rangeEnd=2269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_1497-1525",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1497-1525",
      "markText": "她希望自己被囚禁，那么他就会为了她而来，“你不过是说笑。",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1497&rangeEnd=1525",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1497&rangeEnd=1525"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_10446-10478",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10446-10478",
      "markText": "古来所谓的鱼水之欢和鸳鸯交颈舞。不如说是一条狗在自顾自地撞向树桩",
      "totalCount": 84,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10446&rangeEnd=10478",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10446&rangeEnd=10478"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_5_2492-2510",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2492-2510",
      "markText": "“听说个性强的人难学会另一门语言。”",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_5_3851-3897",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3851-3897",
      "markText": "现代史没有变成史籍，一团乱麻，是个危险的题材，绝不会在他们的时代笔之于书。真实有一千种面相。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3851&rangeEnd=3897",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3851&rangeEnd=3897"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_7_5332-5380",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5332-5380",
      "markText": "坐在他身上使她感到极其怪异，仿佛有一个蒙着布的活塞，或是一条挥打着的返祖般的尾巴，在轻轻棰击她。",
      "totalCount": 78,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=22799676&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5332&rangeEnd=5380",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8c532750715be53c8c53f43?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5332&rangeEnd=5380"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "22799676_10_1486-1572",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1486-1572",
      "markText": "童话故事里往往是少年得志，这种结局自有几分道理。在那最敏感的年龄得到的，始终与你同在。只有这段时间，才可以让任何人经营出超凡的事物，而它们也将以其独有的方式跟生命一样持久。",
